    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolute gold to me. It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs like a dream, and has been super well-maintained over the years. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is reliable and ready to go! Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54B32 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, producing 333 hp with a 7,900 RPM redline. This chassis is paired with a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed: the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates, and the VANOS system was recently overhauled with upgraded seals and a cryo-treated hub. The valve clearances were shimmed to factory specifications within the last 5,000 miles. Suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers. While the exterior shows minor road-wear consistent with its age, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response are sharp, making this an ideal candidate for a purist collector or spirited driver.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
