    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2019 Executive Sport Sedan that perfectly balances performance with daily utility. This vehicle has been garage-kept and remains in impressive mechanical and cosmetic shape. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no rips or stains, and the dual-zone climate control and infotainment system function flawlessly. Recent service includes a fresh synthetic oil change, a new cabin air filter, and a comprehensive multi-point inspection confirming the brakes and suspension are in excellent working order. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, ensuring a smooth, confident ride for miles to come. This is a non-smoker vehicle with a clean title and a full service history available for review. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers the reliability you expect from a well-cared-for machine.",
      "price": 36450.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
